{"tid":211621,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[旅遊新手］香草夜晚機到東京成田之困惑","createTime":"2017-04-21T18:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T19:10:45.000Z","uid":81286,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05235f62c5c25936dd61eee6130a007fe791431f","tid":211621,"uid":81286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:09:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的，6月做廿四孝男友帶女友去東京玩，book左香草航空，<br />\n就預計就9:10pm到成田，京成本線最尾班車好似係10:30pm<br />\n諗緊 （a）落機果日book成田附近酒店住一晚 第日先出返出面住好 （依個option住既地點就flexible d)<br />\n定係 （b）狗沖尾班車出去 （如果依個option既話應該會住上野附近）<br />\n<br />\n我同女友傾過 佢就prefer （b)多d 但係我驚如果趕唔到尾班車就仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇ching教教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小弟正值黃金年齡 重未想死住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61784f15600e1c8f645a8c3ffcd39f9e130f63e2","tid":211621,"uid":33727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:29:29.000Z","msg":"京成Sky Access 尾班車 <br />\n空港第２ビル 22:51&rarr;京成上野 23:47<br />\n<br />\n京成巴士Tokyo Shuttle 尾班車<br />\nT3 23:10&rarr;東京站八重洲口 0:27<br />\n再轉JR去上野都仲有車 尾班車0:57"},{"pid":"718d63a8f82a86f1ec286f7d67500a5bd3379989","tid":211621,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"京成本線: 22:42 <br />\n京成Access特急: 22:51 <br />\nJR: 23:02"},{"pid":"495832f5c8ca05d89c08ddd59d40b045943299a5","tid":211621,"uid":49868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:31:29.000Z","msg":"趕唔到尾班車就要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你條命真值錢<br />\n<br />\nbtw係廿四孝就咪柒夜機到喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0064288507087ddeeea59e437b3247ea911cc7c6","tid":211621,"uid":26506,"like":0,"